(54, 'Man alleges that Oguta LGA in Imo state is owing him N900k since 2007', 'http://www.lindaikejisblog.com/2015/10/man-alleges-that-oguta-lga-in-imo-state.html', 'Uncategorized', NULL, '<div class="separator" style="clear: both; text-align: center;"><img border="0" src="http://3.bp.blogspot.com/-Pc-2DAlI49Q/VhKXnQuZrBI/AAAAAAAG3E0/C3ZOsMb_y9E/s1600/1.jpg" /><img border="0" src="http://4.bp.blogspot.com/-JGhRYkHcYc8/VhKXoFKpgeI/AAAAAAAG3E8/RTNu1_slhkE/s1600/3.jpg" /></div>The man shares his story below...<br /><blockquote class="tr_bq">My name is Mr. Orjika Emma C. K., In 2007, The Oguta LGA of Imo State  awarded me a contract to supply books for primary schools. The total  project amount was N1,050,000. I was given a down payment of N150,000  and I was owed N900,000. Ever since then they have refused to pay me. I  have tried everything possible to no avail. I reached out to a barrister  who told me to first pay him 30% of the money before he would help him. I  refused to pay because it was both unethical and unprofessional. Please  help me.<br /><a name=''more''></a></blockquote><div class="separator" style="clear: both; text-align: center;"><a href="http://3.bp.blogspot.com/-6O88pm3kT2k/VhKXzsceIOI/AAAAAAAG3FM/IE9-JI-aUNg/s1600/7.jpg" imageanchor="1" style="margin-left: 1em; margin-right: 1em;"><img border="0" src="http://3.bp.blogspot.com/-6O88pm3kT2k/VhKXzsceIOI/AAAAAAAG3FM/IE9-JI-aUNg/s1600/7.jpg" /></a><a href="http://2.bp.blogspot.com/-Qgy5L3Ag87A/VhKX0hRb43I/AAAAAAAG3FU/l1XIPSBnQnA/s1600/8.jpg" imageanchor="1" style="margin-left: 1em; margin-right: 1em;"><img border="0" src="http://2.bp.blogspot.com/-Qgy5L3Ag87A/VhKX0hRb43I/AAAAAAAG3FU/l1XIPSBnQnA/s1600/8.jpg" /></a></div><br /><div class="separator" style="clear: both; text-align: center;"></div>', '2015-10-05 21:28:29', '2015-10-05 16:37:00', 8, 'http://3.bp.blogspot.com/-Pc-2DAlI49Q/VhKXnQuZrBI/AAAAAAAG3E0/C3ZOsMb_y9E/s1600/1.jpg', NULL, NULL, 'http://www.lindaikejisblog.com/2015/10/man-alleges-that-ogu