in bed, here’s the immediate appropriate course of action: Find a sympathetic woman and get her to teach you. All women think they’re secret sexperts. If you come across like a guy who’s willing to learn, we’d be happy to turn you out, baby.</p>\n<p style="text-align: justify;"><strong>5. We’re over you.</strong></p>\n<p style="text-align: justify;">Want to know if a relationship is over? Have sex. There’s no hiding true feelings when the clothes come off and the boning starts.</p>\n<p style="text-align: justify;">We’ve been <a href="http://www.yourtango.com/dating">dating</a> for a while. We’ve gotten a little distant lately. We don’t return your calls and texts as quickly as we used to. And exactly what were we up to when we stayed out until 3 AM with our girlfriends last Saturday night? We’re just not that into you anymore.</p>\n<p style="text-align: justify;"><strong>It’s not you — it’s us. Instead of hanging around and banging your head against our cervical walls, take your sex act on to another woman who will appreciate what you do when you get down.</strong></p>\n<p style="text-align: justify;">This post orignally appeared on Your Tango: <a href="http://www.yourtango.com/200940087/5-reasons-why-man-bad-bed" target="_blank">5 Reasons Men Are Awful in Bed</a></p>\n</div>\n</div><p>The post <a rel="nofollow" href="http://www.thetrentonline.com/5-reasons-men-are-freakin-awful-in-bed-according-to-women-2/">5 Reasons Men Are Freakin&#8217; AWFUL In Bed (According to Women)</a> appeared first on <a rel="nofollow" href="http://www.thetrentonline.com">The Trent</a>.</p>\n', '2015-10-03 08:15:24', '2015-10-03 07:15:22', 10, NULL, NULL, NULL, 'http://www.thetrentonline.com/5-reasons-men-are-freakin-awful-in-bed-according-to-women-2/', '2015-10-03 08:17:41', 1),
