ext-align: justify;"><strong>3. Start with your hands.</strong></p>\n<p style="text-align: justify;">OK, so that first tip was quite general and you may be eager to just learn some specific tips. What I want to do now is show you how to use your hands on your man when in bed.</p>\n<p style="text-align: justify;">Here are 3 awesome things your man will greatly appreciate that you can do with your hands:</p>\n<ul style="text-align: justify;">\n<li><em>Try massaging him before sex.</em> Most foreplay usually consists of of kissing and heavy petting before getting down to the act itself. A really nice change that your man will love is giving him a massage first before you do anything else. <strong>Pro tip: </strong>Doing it with coconut oil will make it way more enjoyable for him.</li>\n<li><em>Don’t forget about some hand action.</em> Using your hands on his penis is simple, yet he will greatly appreciate and enjoy it. But rather than just grabbing his shaft and paying most of your attention to it (as it’s easy to hold), you should focus most of your attention on the top of his penis as it’s by far the most sensitive part and the area that he will get most pleasure from.</li>\n<li><em>Don’t be afraid to play with his balls during sex.</em> If you’re in a position like cowgirl, then reach behind yourself while he’s thrusting in and out and gently massage his balls.</li>\n</ul>\n<p style="text-align: justify;"><strong>4. Experiment with positions.</strong></p>\n<p style="text-align: justify;">The easiest way to learn how to be good in bed is to just add a few new positions to your repertoire. There are an almost endless amount of different positions that you can try out with your man. Here are few to get you started:</p>\n<ul style="text-align: justify;">\n<li><em>The Rodeo.</em> Performing the rodeo is very similar to performing the cowgirl position on your man. To do it, your man needs to lie down on his back and you need to straddle him on your knees, facing away from