(93, ' OJ Simpson denies sleeping with Kris Jenner ', 'http://www.lindaikejisblog.com/2015/11/oj-simpson-denies-sleeping-with-kris.html', 'Uncategorized', NULL, '<div class="separator" style="clear: both; text-align: center;"><a href="http://4.bp.blogspot.com/-vXyZ71LdvqE/VjjinfhxTnI/AAAAAAAHMU8/LwYh2aBL3A4/s1600/Screen%2BShot%2B2015-11-03%2Bat%2B10.11.48%2BAM.png" imageanchor="1" style="margin-left: 1em; margin-right: 1em;"><img border="0" height="343" src="http://4.bp.blogspot.com/-vXyZ71LdvqE/VjjinfhxTnI/AAAAAAAHMU8/LwYh2aBL3A4/s400/Screen%2BShot%2B2015-11-03%2Bat%2B10.11.48%2BAM.png" width="400" /></a></div>OJ Simpson may not be Khloe Kardasshian''s father after all because the jailed former athlete has denied ever sleeping with Kris Jenner. I''m sure you all know there is a long standing urban legend that O.J. might actually be Khloe''s father. He''s shut down the rumors once and for all...<br /><br /><a href="https://www.blogger.com/null" name="more"></a>A former prison guard at O.J''s jail is writing at tell all book called ''Guarding the Juice'' and told Page Six when asked about the long standing rumors, O.J. replied,<br /><br /><blockquote>“I would never do that to my friend Bob [Kardashian, who was Simpson’s lawyer]. I would never tap Kris.”</blockquote>', '2015-11-03 20:06:54', '2015-11-03 17:42:00', 8, 'http://4.bp.blogspot.com/-vXyZ71LdvqE/VjjinfhxTnI/AAAAAAAHMU8/LwYh2aBL3A4/s400/Screen%2BShot%2B2015-11-03%2Bat%2B10.11.48%2BAM.png', NULL, NULL, 'http://www.lindaikejisblog.com/2015/11/oj-simpson-denies-sleeping-with-kris.html', '2015-11-03 20:06:54', 0),
(94, 'DPRecords Presents Adam & Eve by their signed act A.D.O', 'http://www.lindaikejisblog.com/2015/11/dprecords-presents-adam-eve-by-their.html', 'Uncategorized', NULL, '<div class="separator" style="clear: both; text-align: center;"><a href="http://2.bp.blogspot.com/-8kyJo6gjYko/VjjhFD8aFyI/AAAAAAAHMUo/EPvDCNk7Too/s1600/1.jpg" imageanchor="1" style="margin-left: 1em; margin-right: 1em;"><img border="0" src="http://2.bp.blogspot.com/-8kyJo6gjYko/VjjhFD8aFyI/AAAAAAAHMUo/EPvDCNk7Too/s1600/1.jpg" /></a></div>Augustine Otasowie Omokaro (born in the 80ths), goes by the stage name A.D.O, was born, bred and raised in Nigeria. Lived in Edo state before moving to Lagos apapa queens barrack ike at a very tender age. Music from the get go has always been his motivation. He''s a Nigerian rap/hip hop artist Based in Canada.<br /><br /><a name=''more''></a><br /><div class="separator" style="clear: both; text-align: center;"><a href="http://4.bp.blogspot.com/-Ll8BN19Sifg/VjjhFsHTpsI/AAAAAAAHMUs/41Y40qk-5VU/s1600/unnamed.jpg" imageanchor="1" style="margin-left: 1em; margin-right: 1em;"><img border="0" height="400" src="http://4.bp.blogspot.com/-Ll8BN19Sifg/VjjhFsHTpsI/AAAAAAAHMUs/41Y40qk-5VU/s400/unnamed.jpg" width="303" /></a></div><br />As a child developing mentally and physically into a man he never  thought of doing music because of the hurdles and thunderstorms  associated with beat riding,  musical productions and promotions. In  Africa, most  people never got the privilege to do what they loved doing  automatically becoming a dream chaser because of what our parents made  us  be but one thing he did notice about his inner self right from  inception has always been his love for good music. Music got him  tripping when the bread wasn''t coming. always loved being around and  watching musicians performing. Dope beats banging with lyrics soaked in  every veins of the artist,  it was like a glorious moment for him.   Seeing, watching and learning the birth of good music from the claps  Goin way back to the beats,  the artist, production and mastering.  moving to Canada was a game changer life wasn’t easy getting to know  what it feels like being away from home and meeting new people from  deffrent countries. <br /><br />When he first moved to Canada, the first friend he had was a Canadian artist  who was very cool with him trying to upload  the map of the city into his medulla  but at that time he had a studio at home that he would always take him to and he will just sit there and watch him and his friend record tracks on tracks but sometimes he ask them for a pillow to sleep at the studio because he was very shy at that time going into, getting behind that huge phantom mic just to record a couple of tracks. <br />He recorded a few tracks back then and asked his friend who had the studio to help him mix and master just for his own listening. <br /><br />He has always been a shy type. Felt his music was for his ears only until one day when  his song was actually played out to a few friends who never saw him doing his thing as per music but when they did every one encouraged him  to do, at that time he thought they were laughing at him not until one day when he had one of his friend a Canadian artist who was working on his album called him up for features and he was really surprised and shocked after that he developed total interest in what he was known for as per sense of music which is to rap and flow in Edo and English language. <br /><br />His interest in the music industry is to bring his people (Benin) close to the music industry if have been blessed with the talent it took him so many years trying to be what he wasn’t made for before it got to a point in his life that he couldn’t escape it all but to let go. <br /><br />He finally saw himself loving music more and more to a delivery point being an artist wasn’t by choice as he was born to do this. <br /><br />As a human he enjoy all type of music because he grew up knowing that music is Life and through bad / good times music has always been his energy, his blood and also enjoyed being around people who have something productive to talk about. A.D.O is an easy going guy with a big heart of love that revives human soul. <br /><br />He''s type of music is breeding  old school,  cultural music and modern days hip hop and RnB together have worked with a lot of Canadian artist even before he even thinks of releasing a song of his own.<br /><br />Now as it goes great , he has decided to brand the story of Adam and Eve into mind blowing music titled "ADAM AND EVE" produced by "Apya"  mastered "Dr. Rad" . <br /><br /><a href="http://ow.ly/U505L" target="_blank">Click Here To Download A.D.O - Adam &amp; Eve</a><br /><br /><a href="http://ow.ly/U505L" target="_blank">http://ow.ly/U505L</a>', '2015-11-03 20:06:54', '2015-11-03 17:32:00', 8, 'http://2.bp.blogspot.com/-8kyJo6gjYko/VjjhFD8aFyI/AAAAAAAHMUo/EPvDCNk7Too/s1600/1.jpg', NULL, NULL, 'http://www.lindaikejisblog.com/2015/11/dprecords-presents-adam-eve-by-their.html', '2015-11-03 20:06:54', 0),
