 winner is Hyundai Elantra 2015 and N1, 000,000.</span></span></div><div class="MsoNormal" style="background: white none repeat scroll 0% 0%; line-height: 16.95pt; margin-left: 12pt;"><br /></div><div class="separator" style="clear: both; text-align: center;"><span style="font-size: small;"><span style="font-family: inherit;"><a href="http://1.bp.blogspot.com/-Ehfqxz9OVR4/VjjUz5m9JYI/AAAAAAAHMS8/tDoc-D94Ezs/s1600/3.png" imageanchor="1" style="margin-left: 1em; margin-right: 1em;"><img border="0" src="http://1.bp.blogspot.com/-Ehfqxz9OVR4/VjjUz5m9JYI/AAAAAAAHMS8/tDoc-D94Ezs/s1600/3.png" /></a></span></span></div><div style="background: white none repeat scroll 0% 0%; line-height: 16.95pt; margin: 0cm 0cm 15pt;"><span style="font-size: small;"><span style="font-family: inherit;"><span>Our primary aim is to make the dreams of these young artistes a reality by giving them the orientation and encouragement, keep them focused in a reality show setting.</span></span></span></div><div style="background: white none repeat scroll 0% 0%; line-height: 16.95pt; margin: 0cm 0cm 15pt;"><span style="font-size: small;"><span style="font-family: inherit;"><span>SUO Raise Your Voice will serve the Nigeria Music industry with 10 episodes and their promos with votes that will be cast on social, web and mobile platforms in Nigeria.</span></span></span></div><div style="background: white none repeat scroll 0% 0%; line-height: 16.95pt; margin: 0cm 0cm 0.0001pt;"><span style="font-size: small;"><span style="font-family: inherit;"><span>The format is completely new as we have moved away from the typical episodic flow of the reality shows or elimination rounds giving the power to the audience without the involvement of any judges.</span></span></span></div><div style="background: white none repeat scroll 0% 0%; line-height: 16.95pt; margin: 0cm 0cm 0.0001pt;"><br /></div><div style="background: white none repeat scroll 0% 0%; line-height: 16.95pt; margin: 0cm 0cm 0.0001pt;"><span style="font-