(110, 'Meet this Halloween mad family (photos)', 'http://www.lindaikejisblog.com/2015/11/meet-this-halloween-mad-family-photos.html', 'Arts and Life,Photo News,,', NULL, '<div class="separator" style="clear: both; text-align: center;"><a href="http://3.bp.blogspot.com/-tOeC6ZYaJak/Vji7o3hdauI/AAAAAAAHMOs/uZf_p6eiu08/s1600/5.jpg" imageanchor="1" style="margin-left: 1em; margin-right: 1em;"><img border="0" src="http://3.bp.blogspot.com/-tOeC6ZYaJak/Vji7o3hdauI/AAAAAAAHMOs/uZf_p6eiu08/s1600/5.jpg" /></a></div>Halloween is a time for people to indulge their inner spookiness but one  family has raised the bar by giving their home a complete horror  makeover. The Waltons of Preston went all out to make it extra special,by spending £20,000 to convert their house into a  ‘Zombie Apocalypse’, with rampaging corpses smashing up a crashed car on  the drive and a cornucopia of body parts within. This  House of Terror is thought to be the most decorated Halloween-inspired  home in Britain. More pics after the cut<br /><br /><a name=''more''></a><br /><br /><div class="separator" style="clear: both; text-align: center;"><a href="http://2.bp.blogspot.com/-DdOrlcHyU58/Vji7Cx2YJvI/AAAAAAAHMOk/Qegh2W6t_CA/s1600/6.jpg" imageanchor="1" style="margin-left: 1em; margin-right: 1em;"><img border="0" src="http://2.bp.blogspot.com/-DdOrlcHyU58/Vji7Cx2YJvI/AAAAAAAHMOk/Qegh2W6t_CA/s1600/6.jpg" /></a></div><br />They have been planning this year’s display for ten months and even  travelled to America to source some of the exhibits. Five temporary  rooms have been added to the family home, including a ‘Zombie’s House’, a  ‘Dracula’s Lair’, an ‘Exorcist room’ and a ‘Haunted Carnival’.<br /><br />The display is open to the public for free, while visitors will be invited to make a donation to Cancer Research.<br /><div class="separator" style="clear: both; text-align: center;"><a href="http://2.bp.blogspot.com/-Ed3tRX5LwyQ/Vji6bT7HCYI/AAAAAAAHMNE/jVO8PM2aqjM/s1600/4.jpg" imageanchor="1" style="margin-left: 1em; margin-right: 1em;"><img border="0" src="http://2.bp.blogspot.com/-Ed3tRX5LwyQ/Vji6bT7HCYI/AAAAAAAHMNE/jVO8PM2aqjM/s1600/4.jpg" /></a></div><div class="separator" style="clear: both; text-align: center;"><img border="0" height="400" src="http://4.bp.blogspot.com/-uUCMJ5qjaoo/Vji6b-tVBVI/AAAAAAAHMNI/ILK_hSKw7kQ/s400/1.jpg" width="266" /><img border="0" height="400" src="http://4.bp.blogspot.com/-C6uWp90ivw4/Vji6c-6ap-I/AAAAAAAHMNU/yDVCG-IHwQY/s400/2.jpg" width="281" /></div><div class="separator" style="clear: both; text-align: center;"><a href="http://3.bp.blogspot.com/-Hc-6cCOG4Ck/Vji6diz32nI/AAAAAAAHMNY/flMP6LCF-Fo/s1600/3.jpg" imageanchor="1" style="margin-left: 1em; margin-right: 1em;"><img border="0" height="426" src="http://3.bp.blogspot.com/-Hc-6cCOG4Ck/Vji6diz32nI/AAAAAAAHMNY/flMP6LCF-Fo/s640/3.jpg" width="640" /></a></div><div class="separator" style="clear: both; text-align: center;"></div><div class="separator" style="clear: both; text-align: center;"><a href="http://3.bp.blogspot.com/-VAJGGONoUJU/Vji6gajs-KI/AAAAAAAHMN0/gdG2wT53aiA/s1600/6.jpg" imageanchor="1" style="margin-left: 1em; margin-right: 1em;"><img border="0" height="416" src="http://3.bp.blogspot.com/-VAJGGONoUJU/Vji6gajs-KI/AAAAAAAHMN0/gdG2wT53aiA/s640/6.jpg" width="640" /></a></div><div class="separator" style="clear: both; text-align: center;"><a href="http://2.bp.blogspot.com/-FOCi9W46RqM/Vji6iVSuRKI/AAAAAAAHMN8/bsjkD0T7XAQ/s1600/7.jpg" imageanchor="1" style="margin-left: 1em; margin-right: 1em;"><img border="0" height="426" src="http://2.bp.blogspot.com/-FOCi9W46RqM/Vji6iVSuRKI/AAAAAAAHMN8/bsjkD0T7XAQ/s640/7.jpg" width="640" /></a><a href="http://1.bp.blogspot.com/--xT_fKzxbI0/Vji6kEsFr8I/AAAAAAAHMOI/NOQiCy9t9h4/s1600/8.jpg" imageanchor="1" style="margin-left: 1em; margin-right: 1em;"><img border="0" height="416" src="http://1.bp.blogspot.com/--xT_fKzxbI0/Vji6kEsFr8I/AAAAAAAHMOI/NOQiCy9t9h4/s640/8.jpg" width="640" /></a></div><div class="separator" style="clear: both; text-